ProtoTheorem:
. "Let $P_1$ $P_2, $\dots, $P_n$ \dots\ be propositions, one 
   for each positive integer, such that \begin{alist} \item 
   $P_1$ is true$$ \item for each positive integer $n$ $P_n$ 
   implies $P_{n+1}$ \end{alist} Then $P_n$ is true for each 
   positive integer $n$"
